@page "/contact"

<PageTitle>PureWave | Contact</PageTitle>
<HeadContent>
    <meta name="description" content="Get in touch with PureWave. Reach out with a support query or a general enquiry and we'll get back to you." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="PureWave | Contact" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Get in touch with PureWave for support queries or general enquiries about home theatre consultancy." />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://www.purewaveacoustic.co.za/contact" />
</HeadContent>

<section class="page-intro">
    <span class="section-tag">Contact</span>
    <h1>Get in touch — we'll point you in the right direction.</h1>
    <p>
        Whether you have a question about a plan, need help deciding where to start, or just want to talk through a room problem,
        PureWave is straightforward to reach. Use the address that fits your situation best.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="section-block">
    <div class="contact-card-grid">
        <article class="contact-card">
            <span class="section-tag">Support</span>
            <h2>Something not working the way you expected?</h2>
            <p>
                Use this address for anything related to an existing engagement — follow-up questions, tuning adjustments,
                or a concern about a recommendation. If you are already a client and need a second look at something, this is the right place.
            </p>
            <a class="contact-email" href="mailto:query@purewaveacoustic.co.za">query@purewaveacoustic.co.za</a>
        </article>

        <article class="contact-card">
            <span class="section-tag">General Enquiries</span>
            <h2>Not sure where to start, or just want more information?</h2>
            <p>
                Use this address for anything else — questions about plans, pricing context, whether remote consultancy is the right fit,
                or anything you want to understand before committing. No question is too early.
            </p>
            <a class="contact-email" href="mailto:purewave@purewaveacoustic.co.za">purewave@purewaveacoustic.co.za</a>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="comparison-band">
    <div>
        <span class="section-tag">Ready to go further?</span>
        <h2>The intake questionnaire is the fastest way to get a useful answer.</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        If you already have a room in mind and want specific guidance, the intake form gives PureWave everything needed
        to come back with something practical — rather than a generic reply.
    </p>
    <a class="button-primary" href="/intake">Start the intake</a>
</section>
